room_title: Escape room "The Missing Starlet" by Escape Room Lafayette in Lafayette
room_address: 2429 W Congress St Suite C Lafayette, LA 70506
room_description: Step back in time to the 1950’s, the Hollywood Golden Age. Among the glitz and glamour of Hollywood, there has been a crisis: a missing starlet! This up-and-coming movie star has suddenly disappeared under mysterious circumstances. You have been brought in to investigate her disappearance and been given access to the last place she was seen, her private dressing room. Will that be enough to solve the mystery? It’s up to you.
